    "description": "<p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\">The Priest is able to perform minor miracles as long as they keep their faith. They gain the Minor Miracle Ability.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\">Each time the Priest uses a Miracle Ability they can’t do so it any more. Once at the start of each day they make a prayer and make a </span><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><a class=\"link-opacity-50-hover\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(110, 168, 254);text-decoration:underline;cursor:pointer\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">DT</span></a></span></span><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"> 25 </span><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><a class=\"link-opacity-50-hover\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(110, 168, 254);text-decoration:underline;cursor:pointer\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">SPI</span></a></span></span><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"> </span><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><a class=\"link-opacity-50-hover\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(110, 168, 254);text-decoration:underline;cursor:pointer\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">ATTRIBUTE TEST</span></a></span></span><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"> which can’t be modified in any other way, on a success they can use miracles again. They can repeat the Test each following day where they reduce the </span><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"><a class=\"link-opacity-50-hover\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(110, 168, 254);text-decoration:underline;cursor:pointer\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">DT</span></a></span></span><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'\"> by 5 until they succeed. Alternatively if the Priest Character acts well within their believes or played well the GM may grant them the Miracle again without rolling.</span></p><p>@UUID[Compendium.reclaim-the-realm.coreAbilities.Item.EQRI3889dQW5cdGJ]{Minor Miracle}</p>",
